@startuml Melihat Dashboard

skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam DefaultFontStyle bold
skinparam DefaultFontSize 25

skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderThickness 2
skinparam SequenceParticipantBorderThickness 10
skinparam SequenceArrowThickness 5

scale 1.3

actor Pelapor

boundary "Halaman Dashboard" as DashboardUI
control "Dashboard" as Dashboard
entity "Data Laporan" as Laporan
entity "Data Perbaikan" as Perbaikan

Pelapor -> DashboardUI : Mengakses Halaman Dashboard

DashboardUI -> Dashboard : Meminta Data Dashboard

Dashboard -> Laporan : Mengambil Data Dashboard

Laporan --> Dashboard : Data Dashboard

Dashboard --> DashboardUI : Menampilkan Dashboard


== Laporan Aktif ==

Pelapor -> DashboardUI : Memilih Tab Laporan Aktif

DashboardUI -> Dashboard : Meminta Data Laporan Aktif

Dashboard -> Laporan : Mengambil Data Laporan Aktif

Laporan --> Dashboard : Data Laporan Aktif

Dashboard --> DashboardUI : Menampilkan Daftar Laporan Aktif

Pelapor -> DashboardUI : Memilih Salah Satu Laporan

DashboardUI -> Dashboard : Meminta Detail Laporan

Dashboard -> Laporan : Mengambil Detail Laporan

Laporan --> Dashboard : Detail Laporan

Dashboard -> Perbaikan : Mengambil Status Laporan

Perbaikan --> Dashboard : Status Laporan

Dashboard --> DashboardUI : Menampilkan Detail Laporan

Dashboard --> DashboardUI : Menampilkan Status Laporan


